description: Rare new construction 3 bed 3.5 ba townhouse with beautiful fenced yard, private patio & 3 decks!  Perfectly situated in South Boston's coveted City Point neighborhood just steps to the beach, & short walk to broadways restaurant shops & cafe's. This meticulously designed townhouse boasts high ceilings, masterful finish carpentry, high end finishes throughout. The main floor gets amazing light & is perfect for entertaining with a sprawling open concept Living Kitchen dining area. The Stunning chefs kitchen features thermador appliances, custom cabinetry, marble countertops w waterfall, 9 ft island with breakfast bar. The primary bedroom features a spa like en suite bath and beautiful private deck to enjoy your morning coffee. Both guest bedrooms feature en suite baths, with a king size guest bed also boastin private deck. Downstairs, a bonus room works well as a 2nd living room, or could function as home gym/ work space. One of a kind outdoor space for families, pets, and entertaining!
